 <span data-ttu-id="5ea47-102">次の条件下では、実行時に <xref:System.OverflowException> がスローされます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5ea47-102">An <xref:System.OverflowException> is thrown at run time under the following conditions:</span></span>  
  
